cs.SE, cs.PL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.SD 

This paper discusses the use of different diff algorithms in Git, which is a version control system commonly used in software engineering. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.SE (Software Engineering). The paper also involves analyzing code changes, which could fall under cs.PL (Programming Languages) and cs.SD (Software Development). The use of metrics and analysis techniques could also relate to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
